'''MOG PETTOUN DOVORUNK GOROZ ASA'''
''Mog mhnonnge ek pontti koxi. Ti pettoun dovorteleanv zalear, tantun tel ghalunk goroz asa'', ''nam zalear, ti palon vochonk pavtoli''. He sangnnent zaitem khoreponn ani zaiti zannvai asa mhonn gomta. Amcheach ixttancher ani ixttinnincher nodor marlear, zaite pavtt, dog monxeam kazara adim ekamekachea mogan aslolim tim, thoddo kall kazar zatoch zhogddim kortat mhonn polletanv. Hem humanneak ekuch somzonni amkam mellta ani ti mhonnlear kazar zavop mhonnge ek chal and kazar zavun ravop mhonnge dusri vost. Kazar zavun ravpak zaitem xegunnachi goroz asa. Zaiteam kornneamnim amcho mog amchea sangateak vo amche sangatinnik dakhounk ravpak goroz asa.

Soro boro zatolo zalear taka vell lagta. Tech porim kazara adim dog zann mogan astat tancho Kazari mog favo te porim zaunk vell lagta.

Sonvsari mogak lagon logna-sonvkar gheunk dog zann fuddem sortat zalear, mogacho poilo onubhov somplea uprant, tanchea kallzantlo mog denvot veta ani xekim sompot veta. Dusre vatten, purnn kazari mog dis, mhoine ani vorsam sortat titlo ghott zait veta. Dor eka disa noveo khoxalkaio kazari jivitant distti poddot. Proxn poddlei zalear tancho mog proxnancher zoit vhorta.

